* Shadow Cat slowed to a hovering stop in mid-air. She thought for a second 
on how confused her friends back there must be. She felt stupid,she slapped 
her forhead, and in doing so, let go of Snow Tech's one arm-pit. He dangled 
there in her one arm screaming at her to grab hold before he fell. She 
snapped to her sences and looked down on him, grabbing his other arm pit as 
she did.*

" Uh, i kindda rushed things didn't I?"

* Snow Tech nodded and spoke to her*

" I was wondering when you'd notice that you where, and are, making a fool 
of yourself."

* He smiled as she frowned down at him, wanting to smack him, but afraid of 
letting him fall.*

" You know i could let you fall onto those trees down there and make you 
walk to the fight!"

* He grinned and shook his head*

" What! And let all the joy in your life die with me? I don't think so!"

* She grumbled and turned around, heading back to her friends to apoligize*

" What fun?"

* She landed in front of Prowl and Iron Raptor, putting down Snow Tech down 
and stepping aside, directly in front of Iron Raptor. She hung her head and 
mumbled out her apology.*

" I'm sorry that i ran off like that, my fear surciuts mustta over-ridden my 
logic circuits. I hope that you'll forgive me?"
